      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification via Method of Manufactured Solutions (MMS) or equivalent published benchmark.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent Navier-Stokes solver verified against published MMS benchmarks for incompressible viscous flow. Order-of-accuracy confirmed at 2nd order spatial."
    },
    {
