      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported; discretization error bounded below 5% for hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (coarse 2.1M, medium 4.8M, fine 10.2M elements). GCI for hemolysis index QoI = 3.2%, satisfying the 5% threshold. Achieved level 3 exceeds requirement."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented and traceable to CFD boundary conditions; fluid properties match within 5%.",
      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis tests conducted with bovine blood at 37°C, hematocrit 35±2%. CFD boundary conditions derived directly from published FDA generic pump test protocol. Traceability documented."
