      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) predicted within 25% of experimental mean across operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted NIH compared to experimental measurements at 5 operating points. Mean absolute error 18.4%, within the 25% acceptance criterion. Statistical comparison documented."
