      "rationale": "Primary QoI is normalized index of hemolysis, directly relevant to red blood cell damage and CPB device safety. Secondary QoIs (scalar shear stress, Lagrangian exposure time) mechanistically linked to hemolysis models per Giersiepen-Wurzinger correlation."
